          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "External diameter 160-MeV proton beam 11.1 mm.",
                "Proton fluences measured using a transmission ion",
                " chamber and Faraday cup calibrations were made at",
                " several energies."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "High purity (99.999%) aluminium disks, machined to",
                " 12.7 mm in diameter.",
                "In order to keep the energy loss in the target less",
                " than 2 MeV, two different thicknesses used.",
                "Target parameters and proton numbers for each energy",
                " are the following:",
                "  Incident      Energy   Target    Target Total number",
                " proton energy  loss    thickness  weight  of protons",
                "  (MeV)         (MeV)     (mm)      (g)     (x10**12)",
                "   40.0          1.5      0.5      0.173     2.45",
                "   50.0          1.3      0.5      0.174     4.84",
                "   60.0          1.1      0.5      0.172     4.74",
                "   70.0          1.0      0.5      0.173     4.84",
